file.name: Events.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Events
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /events:
    get:
      summary: Get the events that have occured within the simulation
      responses:
        200:
          description: Got Events
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/events'
              examples:
                events:
                  value: |-
                    [
                        {
                            "transId": "1",
                            "location": "debtor-payment-service"
                        },
                        {
                            "transId": "1",
                            "location": "debtor-send-payment"
                        }
                    ]
components:
  schemas:
    events:
      description: Events
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/event'
    event:
      type: object
      required:
        - transId
        - location
      properties:
        transId:
          type: string
        location:
          type: string
